description:
GUtranFreqRelation:  Table detailing the frequency relations of a UTRAN (UMTS Terrestrial Radio Access Network) cell, including parameters for cell selection and measurement.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the data record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
- Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  Another identifier potentially related to the cell's physical location or equipment.
- Id4:  Another identifier potentially related to the cell's configuration.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- GUtranFreqRelation.endcB1MeasPriority: Measurement priority for eNodeB.
- GUtranFreqRelation.gUtranSyncSignalFrequencyRef: Reference frequency of the UTRAN synchronization signal, including subnetwork and cell information.
- GUtranFreqRelation.deriveSsbIndexFromCell: Boolean indicating if the SSB index is derived from the cell.
- GUtranFreqRelation.connectedModeMobilityPrio: Priority for connected mode mobility.
- GUtranFreqRelation.b1ThrRsrqFreqOffset: Frequency offset for RSRQ threshold on band 1.
- GUtranFreqRelation.threshXHighQ: High quality threshold X.
- GUtranFreqRelation.pMaxNR: Maximum power for NR.
- GUtranFreqRelation.threshXLowQ: Low quality threshold X.
- GUtranFreqRelation.b1ThrRsrpFreqOffset: Frequency offset for RSRP threshold on band 1.
- GUtranFreqRelation.allowedPlmnList: List of allowed PLMNs (Public Land Mobile Networks).
- GUtranFreqRelation.threshXLow: Low threshold X.
- GUtranFreqRelation.threshXHigh: High threshold X.
- GUtranFreqRelation.anrMeasOn: Boolean indicating if ANR (Adjacent Neighbour Relation) measurements are enabled.
- GUtranFreqRelation.gUtranFreqRelationId: Unique identifier of the frequency relation.
- GUtranFreqRelation.cellReselectionSubPriority: Sub-priority for cell reselection.
- GUtranFreqRelation.qRxLevMin: Minimum received level.
- GUtranFreqRelation.cellReselectionPriority: Priority for cell reselection.
- GUtranFreqRelation.qQualMin: Minimum quality.
- GUtranFreqRelation.qOffsetFreq: Frequency offset for quality.
